(2292, 2, 7, 'SIGN_IN', 'Login', 0),
(2293, 2, 7, 'SIGN_UP', 'Register', 0),
(2294, 2, 7, 'START_UP_MESSAGE', 'Welcome to the {config}pagetitle{/config}! {config}pagetitle{/config} - is a multiplayer online game. All players will develop into a single universe. You can invite friends and join forces in an attack on the enemies and defense, to use a unique combat system and its own simulator battles. The Exchange will trade resources, ships and artifacts from other players, research will reveal new technology and more advanced weapons systems. Using a variety of strategies and tactics development, you&#39;ll be able to expand his empire and increase the influence of other galaxies in the name of the main goal - to become the master of {config}pagetitle{/config}. To the development of the empire was in full swing, system-mining resources. When construction ends, or accumulate the required amount of resources to build new buildings in the menu <i> </i> buildings. However, do not forget about the energy. Without energy, none of mine will not be able to extract resources. The achievement system will help you to become a thunderstorm {config}pagetitle{/config}. Follow her tips and your development will be the optimal path. Any questions about the game can be discussed in the <i> </i> chat, feel free to ask, there are always ready to help. Sincerely, your team is {config}pagetitle{/config}', 0),
