(2845, 2, 4, 'LANCER_SHIP_DESC', 'Fast and effective warship, built on the most modern technologies. Equipped with a powerful weapon to cause catastrophic damage to the enemy.', 0),
(2846, 2, 4, 'LANCER_SHIP_FULL_DESC', 'Fast and effective warship, built on the most modern technologies. Equipped with powerful weapons, which can cause catastrophic damage to the enemy. To recharge energy gun ship takes time, so the ship has a poor rate of fire. The ship was designed by scientists as an auxiliary weapon for inflicting massive blow to the enemy, and therefore most effective when combined with the rest of the fleet.', 0),
