(2910, 2, 4, 'BALLISTICS_TECH', 'Ballistic Technology', 0),
(2911, 2, 4, 'BALLISTICS_TECH_DESC', 'Ballistic analyzer operates with precision-guided weapons, increasing the accuracy of direct hits to the enemy units.', 0),
(2912, 2, 4, 'BALLISTICS_TECH_FULL_DESC', 'Technology ballistic analysis allows computer systems to calculate the battle before it starts on the basis of spatial location, performance units and fire paths and trajectories of radiation. This makes it possible to conduct aimed fire and precision throughout the fight. The technology reduces mistakes and falling into the already destroyed units.', 0),
(2913, 2, 4, 'MASKING_TECH', 'Masking Technology', 0),
(2914, 2, 4, 'MASKING_TECH_DESC', 'Technology radio-location creates a masking noise in the analyzer and ballistic guidance systems of enemy fire.', 0),
(2915, 2, 4, 'MASKING_TECH_FULL_DESC', 'Technology radio-location creates a masking noise in the analyzer and ballistic guidance systems of enemy fire. This technology increases the survivability of their units by reducing the firing accuracy of firing guns of the enemy.', 0),
