(2923, 2, 13, 'EXPEDITION_CREDITS_DISCOVERY_1', 'Your researchers found the field of battle. Unfortunately, not all ships are intact and without resources, but in one of the survivors, the researchers found safe {@credits} loans. Congratulations, credits are transferred to your account. The fleet returned to base.', 0),
(2924, 2, 13, 'EXPEDITION_CREDITS_DISCOVERY_2', 'Expedition equipment zapelengovalo strange object. It was the captain&#39;s cabin with an unknown ship callsign working device. Felling cut off from the main ship super-weapon, the researchers surprised, nothing like they have not seen. In general, absolutely safe, the researchers found the {@credits} loans. Congratulations, credits are transferred to your account. The fleet returned to base.', 0),
(2925, 2, 13, 'EXPEDITION_CREDITS_DISCOVERY_3', 'Expedition equipment zapelengovalo strange object. This was double the damaged spaceship with a dead creature unknown race. Under the seat, the researchers found an alien {@credits} loans. Congratulations, credits are transferred to your account. The fleet returned to base.', 0),
(2926, 2, 13, 'EXPEDITION_CREDITS_DISCOVERY_4', 'Expedition equipment zapelengovalo strange object. It was a dead alien pilot, as evidenced by his outfit. Research has shown that the alien died while in the open space in a state of suspended animation {@anabios_years} years, when the life support systems have spent their resources (apparently dumped in open space in some battle.) The clothes found the pilot beacon and call {@credits} loans. Credits are transferred to your account. The fleet returned to base.', 0),
(2927, 2, 13, 'EXPEDITION_CREDITS_DISCOVERY_5', 'Expedition equipment zapelengovalo strange object. It was a little damaged alien craft. The researchers carefully examined it and found something: sneaky aliens hidden in a secret {@credits} loans. Congratulations, credits are transferred to your account. The fleet returned to base.', 0),
(2928, 2, 13, 'EXPEDITION_CREDITS_DISCOVERY_6', 'Your researchers found the field of battle. Unfortunately, not all ships are intact and without resources, but in a secret compartment of one of the ships careful researchers have found the {@credits} loans. Congratulations, credits are transferred to your account. The fleet returned to base.', 0),
