(3034, 2, 3, 'FLEET_MESSAGE_OTHER_RES', 'Alien Fleet ({@fleet}) {@username} {@message} to {@planet} {@coords} reaches your coordinates {@target} {@targetcoords}. Assignment: {@mission}. <br /> Cargo: {@metal} metal {@silicon} Si and {@hydrogen} hydrogen.', 0),
