(3202, 2, 18, 'TARGET_MOON_NOT_DESTROYED', 'Generators Death Stars attacker store energy for the gravity of attack and make the shot on the moon. Shocks, one after another, shaking the satellite, but the Moon remains in place. The satellite is stabilized by releasing the excess energy by gravitational pulses. Power generators, Death Stars are not enough to destroy the moon.', 0),
