(3270, 2, 13, 'NEUTRAL_PLANET_FOUND', 'After long walks on the expanses of the universe, the sensors detected a strange mission activity in the area of ??{@planet}. <br/> approaching nearer, they found that this previously unknown planet of aliens from the rubble of the battle. Apparently someone recently broke a big fleet here. On the orbit of the planet discovered the wreckage: {@metal} metal {@silicon} silicon. Hurry to pick them up, because planet is not stable and will soon be destroyed, except that the planet is known to someone else!', 0),
(3271, 2, 13, 'NEUTRAL_PLANET_DIE', 'It turns out the alien fleet is not in vain as fighting for the planet. In its crust began to show unprecedented strength of the gravitational anomalies and, before scientists had to investigate them, a planet {@planet} collapsed on submateriyu.', 0),
