(3340, 2, 22, 'FIVE_ATTACKER', 'Iron muscles.', 0),
(3341, 2, 22, 'FIVE_ATTACKER_DESC', 'Not all the world will recognize you as their ruler. Build some ships attacking the plan for starting your victorious march across the galaxy.', 0),
(3342, 2, 22, 'FIRST_ENERGY', 'Sun - our friend.', 0),
(3343, 2, 22, 'FIRST_ENERGY_DESC', 'Exploring the solar radiation can try to get her out of energy. Explore energy technology to increase the production of electricity.', 0),
(3344, 2, 22, 'TEN_TRANSPORT', 'Space Truckers.', 0),
(3345, 2, 22, 'TEN_TRANSPORT_DESC', 'For the transport of goods between planets, as well as to gather resources from other planets are best transports. More transports can carry extra supplies of fuel, thereby increasing the range of the fleet.', 0),
(3346, 2, 22, 'FIRST_DEFFENCE', 'Fasten the wall.', 0),
(3347, 2, 22, 'FIRST_DEFFENCE_DESC', 'Galaxy - a dangerous and harsh place. While you surf the fleet of space, on your planet can attack other players. Make them pay for complacency - begin to build defenses.', 0),
