(3349, 2, 22, 'FIRST_ENGINE_DESC', 'To move your ship in space and need reliable moschnye engines. Examining his first engine you&#39;ll be one step closer to the conquest of space.', 0),
(3350, 2, 22, 'FIVE_ROCKET', 'We are not alone, but we are protected.', 0),
