(3396, 2, 25, 'MENU_ACHIEVEMENTS_PAGE_DESC', 'To get the achievements must meet certain requirements. Them immediately after you uvidesh list of awards in the description of accomplishments. Green noted requirements met, red - unfulfilled.', 0),
(3397, 2, 25, 'MENU_BUILD_TITLE', 'Education and housing construction', 0),
(3398, 2, 25, 'MENU_BUILD_DESC', 'To fulfill the achievement of &quot;Protect the environment&quot;, it is necessary to build a solar power station (this structure, the game also known as a building or construction). To build a solar power station, go to the buildings.', 0),
(3399, 2, 25, 'BUILD_SOLAR_TITLE', 'Construction', 0),
(3400, 2, 25, 'BUILD_SOLAR_DESC', '<p /> In order to construct a building must meet all the requirements for its construction and have the necessary amount of resources. <p /> solar power is displayed immediately after the synthesizer hydrogen. Click on the Build Solar Power Plant in front of the description. Scroll down a bit if a button is not visible Build.', 0),
(3401, 2, 25, 'SHOW_ME_TUTORIAL_TITLE', 'Tips', 0),
(3402, 2, 25, 'SHOW_ME_TUTORIAL_DESC ', '<p /> Tips can be turned off by pressing the button in the prompt box <b> </b> Hide. In order to show the tips again, click on a question for the <b> </b> (it is now indicated by the arrow). Click <p /> <b> click </b> Next to continue exploring the game.', 0),
(3403, 2, 25, 'MENU_GALAXY_TITLE', 'Introduction to the galaxy', 0),
(3404, 2, 25, 'MENU_GALAXY_DESC', '<p /> While the solar power station is built, let&#39;s look at a star system, where your planet. I wonder if you have neighbors. Go to the Galaxy.', 0),
(3405, 2, 25, 'MENU_GALAXY_DESC_TITLE', 'View the Galaxy', 0),
(3406, 2, 25, 'MENU_GALAXY_DESC_DESC', '<p /> The universe consists of galaxies OXSAR, which consist of stellar systems. Each system can be located up to 30 planets. <p /> When you view the galaxy consumes 10 hydrogen!', 0),
(3407, 2, 25, 'MENU_CHAT_TITLE', 'Introduction to chat', 0),
(3408, 2, 25, 'MENU_CHAT_DESC', '<p /> For the communication between players and help newcomers to the game have a chat. Let&#39;s see what&#39;s happening now. <p /> Go to Chat.', 0),
(3409, 2, 25, 'MENU_CHAT_DESC_TITLE', 'Chat', 0),
(3410, 2, 25, 'MENU_CHAT_DESC_DESC', '<p /> There are two types of chat - General chat and the alliance. In the general chat can communicate with all players. In a chat alliance - only the players a concrete alliance. You can join an existing alliance to develop and fight together.', 0),
(3411, 2, 25, 'SOLARPLANT_BONUS_TITLE', 'Performed to achieve', 0),
(3412, 2, 25, 'SOLARPLANT_BONUS_DESC', '<p /> At the completion of construction of solar power you fulfilled all requirements to achieve &quot;Protect the environment.&quot; Reward: a second level of solar power and 2 solar satellite. This will provide energy to your planet soon. It&#39;s time to get the reward.', 0),
(3413, 2, 25, 'MENU_FLEET_TITLE', 'Familiarity with Navy', 0),
(3414, 2, 25, 'MENU_FLEET_DESC', 'View and send their ships in flight can be from a page of the fleet. <br /> Go back.', 0),
(3415, 2, 25, 'MENU_FLEET_DESC_TITLE', 'Fleet Overview', 0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` (`phraseid`, `languageid`, `phrasegroupid`, `title`, `content`, `translated`) VALUES
(3416, 2, 25, 'MENU_FLEET_DESC_DESC', 'On the page of the fleet you can see all their ships on this planet and thus sending them to attack, or an expedition to load management and transport to other planets, or simply to move between your planets.', 0),
(3417, 2, 25, 'MENU_SIMULATOR_TITLE', 'Battle simulator', 0),
(3418, 2, 25, 'MENU_SIMULATOR_DESC', '<p /> Soon you will be able to go into space and attack other players. An important component of defeating the enemy - proschityvanie chances of a successful outcome of the battle. To do this you need to combat simulator.', 0),
(3419, 2, 25, 'MENU_SIMULATOR_DESC_TITLE', 'Simulated battle', 0),
(3420, 2, 25, 'MENU_SIMULATOR_DESC_DESC', 'In order to carry out the simplest simulation of the battle - and lead the fleet attacking defender, and then click Simulate <b> </b> at the bottom of the page. Knowing how to simulate the battle will help you in passing the course the young fighter.', 0),
(3421, 2, 25, 'CONTINUE_ACHIV_TITLE', 'Course of the young soldier', 0),
(3422, 2, 25, 'CONTINUE_ACHIV_DESC', '<p /> Now you know a lot about the game. Continued to develop his empire following the instructions of a young soldier Course (just to perform the necessary requirements for the achievements), and very soon you go into space with warships and able to conduct military operations. <p /> Enjoy the game.', 0),
(3423, 2, 25, 'PLANET_CREATION_WAIT_TITLE', 'Waiting for a planet', 0),
(3424, 2, 25, 'PLANET_CREATION_WAIT_DESC', 'Your planet is created, wait a bit and refresh the page.', 0),
(3425, 2, 25, 'SOLARPLANT_CONSTRUCTED_TITLE', 'Completion of construction', 0),
(3426, 2, 25, 'SOLARPLANT_CONSTRUCTED_DESC', '<p /> solar power that you started to build some time ago, probably already been built. Let&#39;s see it. Go to the buildings.', 0),
(3427, 2, 25, 'MENU_GALAXY_COORD_DESC', '<p /> To see the different galaxies and systems, you can enter the desired kordinaty in the input field. The coordinates of the planets appear [X: Y: Z], where X - number of the galaxy, Y - number of stellar systems, Z - number of the planet. <p /> The smaller number of the planet, the planet is closer to the star, the higher the temperature it can be. Temperature affects the production of hydrogen than it is, the less hydrogen is produced. But more energy is generated by solar satellites.', 0),
(3428, 2, 25, 'MENU_GALAXY_COORD_TITLE', 'The coordinates of the planets', 0),
(3429, 2, 8, 'RESEND_ACTIVATION_LABEL', 'Send new message about activated on e-mail', 0),
(3430, 2, 8, 'RESEND_ACTIVATION', 'Send', 0),
(3431, 2, 1, 'PLEASE_ACTIVATE_ACCOUNT', 'Activation of the e-mail not yet implemented. Check please my mail, it sent a letter about activation. This must be done to avoid losing access to the game and be able to recover a forgotten password or change the current if necessary. If you do not got a letter about the activation in the e-mail, ask him zanogo on the Settings page. If the letter does not come after several attempts, change the email on the other also on the Settings page.', 0),
(3432, 2, 25, 'SOLAR_PLANT_WAIT_TITLE', 'Necessary to construct the SES', 0),
(3433, 2, 25, 'SOLAR_PLANT_WAIT_DESC', '<p /> The next step is to build a solar power plant. If you have already started building it, wait for the completion and click <b> </b> Next. Otherwise Start building right now.', 0),
(3434, 2, 18, 'SHIPYARD_POWER', 'Shipyard', 0),
(3435, 2, 18, 'DEFENSE_FACTORY_POWER', 'Equi. plant', 0),
(3436, 2, 12, 'EXCH_TITLE_EXISTS', 'Exchange with the name {@exch_title} already exists!', 0),
(3437, 2, 4, 'PLANET_TEMP_CREATOR_FULL_DESC', 'Allows you to create planetary lighthouse - a temporary dwarf planet to the moon for the deployment of ships. The buildings are constructed on the moon is much faster than conventional moons, but it can be destroyed by the Death Star in every galaxy. After the destruction of the moon at the lighthouse, the new can not be built. Lighthouse entirely self-destructs the gravitational anomaly in 3 weeks (with all the buildings on it, if there is any), the fleet should also be harvested before the destruction. Lighthouse - a planetary set, the moon or a planet may be a beacon to leave at any time if necessary. To create a lighthouse, you must send an artifact in the Navy from the colonizer to the free position.', 0),
(3438, 2, 4, 'PLANET_TEMP_CREATOR_DESC', 'Allows you to create a temporary dwarf planet with a moon for a point dislocation for 3 weeks. On the moon the lighthouse can be built much faster than conventional moons, but it can be destroyed. To create a lighthouse, you must send an artifact in the Navy from the colonizer to the free position.', 0),
(3439, 2, 4, 'PLANET_TEMP_CREATOR', 'Planetary lighthouse', 0),
(3440, 2, 4, 'TRANSMITTER', 'Transmitter', 0),
(3441, 2, 4, 'TRANSMITTER_DESC', 'The heavy transport ship with a huge capacity and a scalable means of propulsion.', 0),
(3442, 2, 4, 'TRANSMITTER_FULL_DESC', 'The heavy transport vessel is built on new developments in today&#39;s engines and hull protection. These technologies have allowed a reasonable survival rate of the transport ship with a huge capacity and scalable high-speed characteristics. Unique motor line-up allows you to update multiple engines, reaching an unprecedented rate for other transports in the empire.', 0),
(3443, 2, 1, 'ARTEFACT_NOT_BUYABLE', 'You can not buy', 0),
(3444, 2, 13, 'TEMP_PLANET_DIE', '{@planet} lighthouse destroyed by the gravitational anomaly.', 0),
(3445, 2, 13, 'TEMP_PLANET_DIE_SUBJ', 'Lighthouse destroyed', 0),
(3446, 2, 10, 'JUMP_SUCCESSFUL_HITCHED', 'Overloading the system with teleportation, something went wrong, but it seems everything is in order.', 0),
(3447, 2, 13, 'RETREAT_TRANSPORT', '{@username} Vehicles overturned on {@planet_from} {@coords_from}. Your fleet ({@fleet}) returns to the {@planet} {@coords}.', 0),
(3448, 2, 13, 'RETREAT_TRANSPORT_SUBJECT', 'Cancel Transport', 0),
(3449, 2, 10, 'CONTROL_EVENT', 'Manage', 0),
(3450, 2, 10, 'FLEET_MESSAGE_HOLDING_FUEL', 'Navy ({@fleet}) belonging to the {@username} {@message} to {@planet} {@coords} is the orbit {@target} {@targetcoords} {@target_username} {@target_message}. <br /> Cargo: {@metal} metal {@silicon} Si and {@hydrogen} hydrogen. Fuel: {@fuel_hydrogen} hydrogen.', 0),
(3451, 2, 10, 'UNLOAD_RESOURCES', 'Unload', 0),
(3452, 2, 10, 'LOAD_RESOURCES', 'Download', 0),
(3453, 2, 10, 'FLEET_MESSAGE_HOLDING', 'Navy ({@fleet}) belonging to the {@username} {@message} to {@planet} {@coords} is the orbit {@target} {@targetcoords} {@target_username} {@target_message}. <br /> Cargo: {@metal} metal {@silicon} Si and {@hydrogen} hydrogen.', 0),
(3454, 2, 1, 'STARGATE_JUMP', 'Teleportation', 0),
(3455, 2, 13, 'STARGATE_JUMP_REPORT', 'Your fleet (%s) have successfully teleported to the %s %s.', 0),
(3456, 2, 13, 'STARGATE_JUMP_REPORT_SUBJECT', 'Teleportation is successful', 0),
(3457, 2, 4, 'IGLA_MORI', 'Needle Mori Coleys', 0),
(3458, 2, 4, 'IGLA_MORI_DESC', 'Allows you to activate the space hopper to move the fleet (including load) through the intergalactic gateway mode giperpoleta. At the same time every hour flight turns into the usual 10 seconds, fuel consumption is reduced in 1000. To activate the hyper flight, you should add needle in the Navy during the redeployment between the moons of the gate.', 0),
(3459, 2, 4, 'IGLA_MORI_FULL_DESC', 'Needle Mori Coleys permeates space and creates a crater with features that let you move the fleet (including load) through the intergalactic gateway mode giperpoleta. In this mode, the fleet travels a distance equivalent to the usual 1-hour flight for 10 seconds, fuel consumption is reduced in 1000. For a long time, the work of this artifact has remained unknown until a group of scholars could not decipher the correspondence of aliens in the computer seized ship alien race. Name of the artifact has been given the names of scientists to unravel its principle. Interstellar gates are locked after use, as in teleportation. To activate the hyper flight, you should add needle in the Navy during the redeployment between the moons of the gate.', 0),
(3460, 2, 13, 'SURVEILLANCE_DETECTED', 'The Navy has found activity in the frequency of the sensor phalanx around the {@coords_planet}, the planet was someone scanned.', 0),
(3461, 2, 13, 'SURVEILLANCE_DETECTED_SUBJ', 'Planet scanned stranger touch phalanx', 0),
(3462, 2, 13, 'ALIEN_HALTING_MSG', 'The Navy received a message from an alien race: Zdravastvuyte, we arrive to the worlds! Alien fleet has taken positions on the orbit {@coords_planet}.', 0),
