(3466, 2, 3, 'FLEET_MESSAGE_ALIEN_OTHER', 'Alien fleet ({@fleet}) flew to the coordinates of {@target} {@targetcoords}. Assignment: {@mission}. <br /> Cargo: {@metal} metal {@silicon} Si and {@hydrogen} hydrogen.', 0),
