(3481, 2, 1, 'PREMIUN_LIST_MAX_SIZE', 'Premium offers cheaper for consumers and more profitable for sellers. Speed ??of delivery is twice as fast, twice as fuel is cheaper. Quality of the product tested intergalactic association guaranteed by the absence of scratches and damage! Maximum shows {@count} lots. After the release of the list item remains in the status of a premium and can be added to the list again.', 0),
