(3487, 2, 1, 'MSG_EXCH_LOT_BACK_RESOURSES', 'At the end of the lot ({@lot}) remained unspent resources, they were returned back to the {@planet}. <br /> Cargo: {@metal} metal {@silicon} Si and {@hydrogen} hydrogen.', 0),
