(3489, 2, 4, 'MOON_LAB', 'Lunar Lab', 0),
(3490, 2, 4, 'MOON_LAB_FULL_DESC', 'Lunar Lab (LL) - is the most perfect structure on the moon and perhaps even throughout the empire, the fruit of labor&#39;s top scientists. Each level of the M 10-fold increases of planetary research laboratory involved in the IIA. This gives the opportunity to research the most time-consuming and not reachable without the LL technology. In addition, each level allows you to use AA on the moon 10% of the power of the planetary mill nanites that allows you to build more and more grandiose buildings. But that&#39;s not all, scientists have found a way to expand through M available fields on the moon for all its greater development.', 0),
(3491, 2, 5, 'MOON_LAB_DESC', 'Moon repeatedly accelerates laboratory research, make available to the moon, planetary mill nanites, adds free fields on the moon.', 0),
(3492, 2, 4, 'MOON_REPAIR_FACTORY_DESC', 'Lunar maintenance hangar is required for the repair of damaged and disposal of unwanted units.', 0),
(3493, 2, 4, 'MOON_REPAIR_FACTORY_FULL_DESC', 'Lunar maintenance hangar is required to perform two operations: 1 - repair of damaged ships and fortifications, 2 - recycling unwanted vehicles and defense to get the resources.', 0),
